<b>Where do I enter my credit card information?</b>
<p>
When you first attempt to activate your account you will be requested to enter your credit
card information. Our system does not store your credit card details but will remember that 
you entered valid payment information and will not request it again. You can continue to
activate the rest of the listings on your account without any hassle. You can also enter your
credit card information under the edit account link.
</p>
</div>

<div class='span5'>
<b>I need to edit or update my credit card information.</b>
<p>
If you need to edit or update your credit card information you will need to go to the link
to edit your account. Under the section on billing information you will be given further
instructions on how to update your information. We will remove your other card details from
our system. You will be charged on the new card for any existing active horse listings.
</p>
</div>
</div>

