<div class='span5'>
<b>What are premium listings and how much do they cost?</b>
<p>
A premium listing is a listing that gets extra visibility on the homepage slideshow. If you
are interested in paying to get your horse featured on the slideshow you will have to contact
us directly to discuss details.
</p>
</div>

<div class='span5'>
<b>Can I pay to get preferred rankings in search results?</b>
<p>
We believe that all horses deserve visibility in search results and we only give preference
to those horse owners who have made the effort to make valuable information, such as 
competition history and pedigree, available to the horse seekers.
</p>
